The paper proposes a new approach for emotion cause extraction using deep memory networks and convolutional neural networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE), which further support these sub-categories.
